subject: Canadian Student Reaching Out
body:
Hi Taras,

I hope this email finds you well.

My name is Vaishika Mathisayan, and I am a finance student at Toronto Metropolitan University - I have attached my resume to provide further clarity on my background.

I found your profile on LinkedIn and I would very much like to learn more about your background. With that said, I would appreciate the opportunity to learn more about your time in the industry, specifically at Moelis.

Please let me know if you would like to have a quick chat in the coming weeks. I'd be happy to work around your schedule.

Kind regards,  
Vaishika
